    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won\u2019t believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
