    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen exhibits exceptional mechanical synchronicity, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous transient response. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement, directing power through a fully serviced limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standard: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe reinforced to ensure lateral rigidity. Zero fluid seepage or bushing deflection. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who prioritizes factory-spec performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint and interior. Full maintenance records included. Like new.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, appearing exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, and the original scent of a new car lingers. Every button, dial, and electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014accompanied by a complete, documented service history from the authorized dealer. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of exceptional caliber, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new, reflecting a history of fastidious maintenance and climate-controlled storage. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a benchmark-quality vehicle. We invite you to inspect this distinguished example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It has been my pride and joy and is still in total showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied this car since day one, so it's flawless inside and out and drives like a dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction and chassis balance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically flawless; the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains rigid with a reinforced rear subframe and pristine bushings, ensuring the legendary MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension geometry performs as intended. The paint retains its factory luster with zero orange peel or road rash, and the interior's Nappa leather remains supple. A concours-level enthusiast vehicle with a comprehensive service dossier.",
      "price": 44500.0,
